February 8,2020.

Lantern Festival, the Fifteenth Day of the first lunar month.

Day 17 of the city closure in Wuhan.

The Gate of Heaven is sealed on the 16th day.

Two days did not see 54 brother dynamic, last night saw a photo of Dr. Li Wenliang, very similar to thin version of him, want to send him to see, by the way, asked him if he recently more text. However, a message in the past was bounced back: The other party account abnormal, has been restricted access. Well, that's not the most embarrassing part. Think of a few common friends, with Li Honghao also sent a message, asked whether there are five four brother's new number: Bang to bounce back, each other... I don't even fuck! Front position down a piece of, the rear of the territory unexpectedly also mourned the wild. I suddenly realized that we were facing two wars at once! And the enemy is nowhere to be seen and nowhere to be seen. Diseases come from the mouth, but the biological virus can be protected against by a mask. Disasters come from the mouth?

Well, someone did, and then they applied, and then some big stuff came up. Let me tell you about my experience. After both posts were blocked, I still haven't registered. The QQ space that records growth has been set to oneself visible, Douban that soaked 12 years also uses to record book video. The official name from 16 years to now, the original intention is only to continue a "literary youth" in the space of the record habit, for self-entertainment and pay homage to the corner. What I'm trying to say is that, in an increasingly virtual age, these binary symbols are all the evidence that a person has ever lived. So in my opinion, being banned is like being murdered. The virus took Dr. Lee's body, but if not through his Weibo, how can we empathize with the fact that he is as ordinary and lovable as we are?

I've already died twice. Seriously, I've been working hard on this number, and I don't want any more problems. But it's not murder I fear, it's faking it so carefully that I become insincere and cynical -- a symptom of this virus. So I admire these two days to die like warriors, their sacrifice is for Dr. Lee's body suffering the most glorious coronation!

And, of course, I know that this battle has only just begun.
